    "In the second baseline model, a standard BiLSTM model is utilized without CRF layer and FastText embedding is used as embedding layer again (BiLSTM FastText) (Fig. 10).",
    "The test results are summarized in Table 7 and overall F1 score and accuracy values for these model and also BiLSTM-CRF with BERT embedding is depicted in Figs.",
